{"tid":458233,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果起咗焚化爐，將堆填區的垃圾運去焚化，再送返去堆填區","createTime":"2017-11-04T16:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T16:24:10.000Z","uid":139993,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"75b091a9326a958a51880f5bc2c9adaf8ed8009f","tid":458233,"uid":139993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:05:30.000Z","msg":"如果起咗焚化爐，你們覺得將堆填區的垃圾運去焚化，再送返去堆填區可唔可行？<br />\n<br />\n我覺得係可行，咁樣就可以減慢堆填區的飽和速度，但點解好似無國家實施？係唔係會引起未知的不良影響？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6597bf3c97e3fc4c315fbc30d2886afee58e69f6","tid":458233,"uid":43013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:10:50.000Z","msg":"成本問題&hellip;<br />\n堆填區啲垃圾唔係就咁用土覆蓋，中間有好多層&hellip;<br />\n如果挖番出來，太浪費時間金錢，成本太高，效益低，咁不如放番喺度&hellip;"},{"pid":"01cfb6b4c2a37b3a73df8995ef1a174454dbb44a","tid":458233,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:11:57.000Z","msg":"Up乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef1291fc644d8a4c37101998987b8881c4f5927","tid":458233,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:19:45.000Z","msg":"唔可行，已經鋪左好多泥<br />\n<br />\n啲有機肉亦都分解得好快，拎去燒根本就燒唔起<br />\n<br />\n要用燃料燒"},{"pid":"e80d855488a4ce7358bd44c0646f07a7391289b0","tid":458233,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:20:09.000Z","msg":"有機物質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9430506321d5d305cc15b92f666954a4872464a4","tid":458233,"uid":139993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:24:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成本問題&hellip;<br />\n堆填區啲垃圾唔係就咁用土覆蓋，中間有好多層&hellip;<br />\n如果挖番出來，太浪費時間金錢，成本太高，效益低，咁不如放番喺度&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n有道理，成世人第一次唔記得考慮錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}